        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/351/431",
        "text": [
          "۳۵۱. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): عِنْدَ تَنَاهِي الشِّدَّةِ تَكُونُ الْفَرْجَةُ، وَعِنْدَ تَضَايُقِ حَلَقِ الْبَلاَءِ يَكُونُ الرَّخَاءُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "351. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: At the extremity of hardship comes relief, and at the tightening of the chains of tribulation comes ease."
          ]
        }
      }
